app_description: Recommend for people like this Want to use a SNS style diary. Want to keep a daily diary in a simple way. Want to use a simple but easy to use diary. Tired of using diary with complicated settings. Simple and beautiful design App is designed to be a simple and easy to use diary. This is an application that embodies simple is best . SNS style diary If you are tired of using a SNS then this app is for you. You can create your own private timeline and write your emotions in a diary. Easy to use Thanks to its simple design and no extra features you can use the app intuitively. You can manage your diary in a fun and stress free manner.
